### YouTube Transcript API Tests
### REST Client for VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@youtubeUrl = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Video Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/video-info?url={{youtubeUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Transcript
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transcript?url={{youtubeUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Description
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/description?url={{youtubeUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

